  "title": "INTERIOR DESIGNER",
  "description": "<h3>Responsibilities:</h3>\n<p>To formulate space planning, concept development and interior design conceptualisation</p>\n<p>To generate 3D Computerised perspective drawings and all construction detail drawings</p>\n<p>To prepare presentation such as design intent, colour scheme and material board</p>\n<p>To prepare for Construction Specification / Design Documentations / Material Selection</p>\n<p>To communicate and liaise with clients, contractors, consultants and project managers on all project matters</p>\n<h3>Requirements:</h3>\n<p>Possess minimum Diploma / Degree in related discipline</p>\n<p>Possess a good knowledge of construction materials and various technical and building codes</p>\n<p>Able to multi-task and meet project schedule</p>\n<p>Able to work independently</p>",
